<id>http://forums.nesdev.com/viewtopic.php?t=11356&amp;p=130101#p130101</id>
<link href="http://forums.nesdev.com/viewtopic.php?t=11356&amp;p=130101#p130101"/>
<title type="html"><![CDATA[Re: convert RGB to NES palette color]]></title>

<content type="html" xml:base="http://forums.nesdev.com/viewtopic.php?t=11356&amp;p=130101#p130101"><![CDATA[
Convert it from RGB to YUV.  Convert UV to phase and amplitude.  Quantize the colors to 4 luma levels, 12 phases and 2 amplitudes.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=4383">psycopathicteen</a> — Sat Jun 21, 2014 2:02 pm</p><hr />
]]></content>
