<content type="html" xml:base="http://forums.nesdev.com/viewtopic.php?t=11356&amp;p=130084#p130084"><![CDATA[
Why do you need to perform this conversion? Are you taking graphics using arbitrary palettes? Are the palettes expected to resemble the actual NES colors? You can try to do the conversion based on what you think the NES palette looks like, but when users have the freedom to use whatever palettes they want you have to ask them to provide the palettes they used so you can convert the graphics properly.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=95">tokumaru</a> — Fri Jun 20, 2014 11:45 pm</p><hr />
